title: Week 16 NFL Recap: Aaron Rodgers the new MVP favorite, Steelers win AFC North, Seahawks win NFC West, other playoff races coming down to final week (Football 12/28)
description:
As they do every Sunday, the Pick Six Superfriends link up late at night to recap all the action in the NFL. Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech cover everything you need to know from Week 16 including Aaron Rodgers surpassing Patrick Mahomes for the best MVP odds as well as the Steelers comeback vs. the Colts, the Browns blowing it vs. the Jets, the Jaguars locking up the #1 pick and much more on postseason races.
Packers-Titans
Steelers-Colts
Jets-Browns
Ravens-Giants
Seahawks-Rams
Panthers-Washington
Cowboys-Eagles
Bears-Jaguars
Chiefs-Falcons
Bengals-Texans
Chargers-Broncos
Winners/Losers
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
